{
  "name": "Avatar of the Beast",
  "type": "feat",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 14th level, you tap into a beastly power that transforms you. As a bonus action, you can enter a rage and gain the following additional benefits until your rage ends:</p><ul><li>Your Strength score becomes 24. When you reach 20th level, your Strength score becomes 30.</li><li>Your size increases to Large.</li><li>Your reach with your claws increases to 10 feet.</li><li>At the start of each turn, you receive temporary hit points equal to half of your barbarian level + your Constitution modifier.</li><li>Using Reckless Attack does not grant other creatures advantage on their attacks against you.</li></ul><p>Once you use this feature, you can't use it again until you finish a long rest.</p>",
